										<PARA>New York City Civil Service Commission adjudications regarding the fitness and discipline of Commissio<BOOKMARK id="0-0-0-14581" name=""/>n employees will be conducted by the Office of Administrative Trials and Hearings. After conducting an adjudication and analyzing all testimony and other evidence, the hearing officer shall make written proposed findings of fact and recommend decisions, which shall be reviewed and finally determined by the Commission.</PARA>
